snippet.title: Quack Invasion - Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2315490/Quack_Invasion/

Pilot mechs as you slaughter hordes of a diverse cast of alien ducks. Build your arsenal from a variety of mechs, weapons and items to survive in ever-changing scenarios.
